    h2 Vertical Grids
    p.
      Grids can also align content vertically as well as horizontally, but by default they align content horizontally.
      To align items vertically use the #[code .grid-vertical] class.
    .grid.grid-vertical.grid-border
      .cell.cell-1 .cell-1
      .cell.cell-1 .cell-1
