  .section
    h2 Grid Alignment
    p.
      Grid cells offten need to be align #[code left/center/right] and #[code top/middle/bottom]
      to create an appearance that looks appealing to the user, this can be done on the grid,
      then onto the cell.
    p.
      By placing an alignment on a horizontal grid we can determine the #[code left/center/right],
      then by placing an alignment on the cell we can determine the #[code top/middle/bottom].
    p.
      This is then reversed when using a vertical grid. By placing an alignment on a vertical
      grid we can determine the #[code top/middle/bottom], then by placing an alignment on the cell we can
      determine the #[code left/center/right].
